                <p><choice><orig>Μνημῖον</orig><reg>μνημεῖον</reg></choice>
               <lb/>
               <choice><orig>Ἄννα</orig><reg>Ἄννης</reg></choice>
                    <choice><orig>Πιθο<lb break="no"/>λάου</orig><reg>Πειθολάου</reg></choice>, τελευ<lb break="no"/>τησάσης με<lb break="no"/>τᾶ καλοῦ ὀνό<lb break="no"/>ματος ἐτῶν<lb/>πεντήκοντα<lb/>πέντε, ἔτους <num value="285">σπε</num>
               <lb/>μηνὸς Δίου πρώτῃ.<lb/>
               <choice><orig>Θάρσι</orig><reg>θάρσει</reg></choice>, <choice><orig>οὺδὶς</orig><reg>οὐδείς</reg></choice> ἀθά<lb break="no"/>νατος. Ἡμέρᾳ Ἡλίου.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Monument of Anna, (daughter) of P(e)itholaos, who died having a good name (at the
                    age) of fifty-five years, in (the) year 285, on the first (day) of (the) month
                    Dios. Be of good cheer, no one (is) immortal. (She died) on the day of (the) Sun
                    (Sunday).</p>
            </div>
